e world came crumbling down. They became aggressive, wandered through the streets killing innocent little kittens and in the end became zombies.\n\nThe best brains in the world, scientists, TV moguls, and producers of soft drinks have put their heads together to resolve the situation.\n\nAnd so they started to broadcast a whole new reality show for the rest of the world.", "short_description": "Reclaim a city from the zombies"}]}, "developer_name": "\u010cen\u011bk \u0160trichel", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://cenda.cz/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "\u010cen\u011bk \u0160trichel", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://cenda.cz/games/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER", "RACING"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "cs", "sk", "es", "pt"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER", "GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1006769306927873"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "777472829514257"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "777472829514257"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1608314420, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "777472829514257"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "5505270406164980", "version": "1.01"}, "id": "1247952805540767", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_applicati